Nollywood actor, Yul Edochie, has advised the former Big Brother season 3 housemate, Leo Babarinde Dasilva, on love and relationship issues. According to the actor, while responding to Leo’s tweet, love chooses who a person falls in love with, expressing that the person hardly chooses who to fall in love with. Leo wrote, “Stop falling in love with people because they are nice to you. Have some self-control. -Advertisement- Edochie responded, “My brother Leo, you can hardly choose who to fall in love with. Na love go choose for you. If e choose, you don enter.”